snippet.title: NIGHTMARE ALLEY (2021) | World Premiere
snippet.description:
Nightmare Alley - World Premiere at Alice Tully Hall (NY)
Directed by Guillermo del Toro and starring Rooney Mara, Bradley Cooper, Cate Blanchett, Willem Dafoe, Toni Collette, Ron Perlman, Tim Blake Nelson...

An ambitious carny with a talent for manipulating people with a few well-chosen words hooks up with a female psychiatrist who is even more dangerous than he is.

#NightmareAlley #RedCarpet.
